    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Isaac's Journey to Beersheba. - Here, where Abraham had spent a long time (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 21:33",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".), Jehovah appeared to him during the night and renewed the promises already given; upon which, Isaac built an altar and performed a solemn service. Here his servants also dug a well near to the tents. ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
